@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJqdXdvbiIsImlhdCI6MTc4MzIyNTUzMSwiZXhwIjoxNzgzMjI5MTMxfQ.Ew8UCBk8oaosFC0kZPCrr28_ve24N4csCDW6SrBgoKY

### 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "juwon",
  "password": "1234"
}

### 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "juwon",
  "password": "1234"
}

### 내 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 프로젝트 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "DevTask 만들기",
  "description": "두 번째 풀스택 프로젝트"
}

### 내 프로젝트 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 프로젝트 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 프로젝트 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/projects/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "DevTask 수정",
  "description": "프로젝트 설명 수정"
}

### 프로젝트 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}